msgid ""
"The value to use for the `~numpy.ufunc.identity` attribute of the resulting "
"object. If specified, this is equivalent to setting the underlying C "
"``identity`` field to ``PyUFunc_IdentityValue``. If omitted, the identity is "
"set to ``PyUFunc_None``. Note that this is _not_ equivalent to setting the "
"identity to ``None``, which implies the operation is reorderable."
